property.name: note
property.value: A simple staggered advance - Stage 1 and 2 switches advance us in sequence until it becomes time to set an ending for a character, "ALONE" "ALEX" "ELISABETH" "HONORADE" and "LUDOVICO". can be triggered at any point to segue to the appropriate ending. (But it's best to wait until we catch outselves in the safety at bar 66 - setting the switch when the player makes the final decision should do it.)
